Company Overview of Cobalt Capital Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Cobalt Capital Management, Inc. is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It manages separate client-focused portfolios. The firm also launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and hedging markets of the United States. The firm invests in the value stocks of companies. It employs long/short equity strategy to make its investments. The firm employs a fundamental analysis to make its investments. It was formerly known as Fusion Capital Management. Cobalt Capital Management, Inc. was founded in December 1994 and is based in New York City with an additional office in Short Hills, New Je...
Cobalt Capital Management, Inc. is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It manages separate client-focused portfolios. The firm also launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and hedging markets of the United States. The firm invests in the value stocks of companies. It employs long/short equity strategy to make its investments. The firm employs a fundamental analysis to make its investments. It was formerly known as Fusion Capital Management. Cobalt Capital Management, Inc. was founded in December 1994 and is based in New York City with an additional office in Short Hills, New Jersey.
